{"tid":166340,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"兩年了，話分開就分開。砌左張圖表達心情","createTime":"2017-03-22T04:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T03:21:27.000Z","uid":34246,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef18c0458d089356a5273cbc83006f413721931","tid":166340,"uid":34246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"同你一齊差唔多兩年。<br />\n一直都好開心，年頭仲一齊去旅行。<br />\n<br />\n但呢個月頭，你就話要同我分開，<br />\n你話原來對我一直無心動既感覺<br />\n只係我對你好，一齊開心先同我一齊<br />\n你仲話而家已經有一個你會對佢心動既男仔<br />\n<br />\n其實近呢半年，我都 feel 到你對我冷淡左<br />\n我有問過你<br />\n你只係話一齊耐左係會無咁熱情<br />\n但我見大家相處仲係好舒服好開心<br />\n所以都不以為意<br />\n<br />\n分開嗰一下<br />\n我有問過你<br />\n究竟有d 乜野係我俾唔到你<br />\n你話係激情<br />\n但我再細問乜野係激情既時候<br />\n你都答唔出<br />\n或者<br />\n可能連你自己都唔知想要乜野吧？<br />\n<br />\n而家其實已經灰完<br />\n接受左件事<br />\n尋晚無聊就砌左福圖出黎玩下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04ZgbrN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04ZgbrN.jpg&h=a15ba9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每一粒Icon 都有故事<br />\n<br />\n但你內心最想要既<br />\n<br />\n對唔住<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知道係咩黎"},{"pid":"430cac20c4721466a5b297c491d8c120541e940c","tid":166340,"uid":28277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:31:24.000Z","msg":"咪on9 啦 呢d值得留戀咩 早走早著咪仲好"},{"pid":"023a093a1a15a527ea8799d3be22d87958babfff","tid":166340,"uid":18863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"一齊得兩年 話無心動就奇啦<br />\n唔好信佢 佢只不過遇到一個更鐘意嘅男仔啫<br />\n藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577662502a7d1adf19d409aab31215ce5222381b","tid":166340,"uid":34246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪on9 啦 呢d值得留戀咩 早走早著咪仲好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打屌醒<br />\n而家好努力咁搣甩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9881618f0abd3f4947ada2f1437d7f373076c7c3","tid":166340,"uid":34246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊得兩年 話無心動就奇啦<br />\n唔好信佢 佢只不過遇到一個更鐘意嘅男仔啫<br />\n藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知係藉口<br />\n<br />\n不過當時<br />\n都仲會俾個藉口自己<br />\n心諗其實佢都唔係咁衰啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b7cd63bb3bd97f563a490bc6821d80639797d7","tid":166340,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:14:57.000Z","msg":"LUIGI巴打<br />\n唔好唔開心 你好有才華 會係一個好男朋友 終有一日遇到你真正既有緣人<br />\n唔好放棄, 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">From 日日追你故ge死忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"fd6a1c21a3d9c75aa24d6d7b59bf51a051f6c615","tid":166340,"uid":59882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:21:50.000Z","msg":"努力生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},{"pid":"c8bbc6c932bf3af7b52740288767a0f9884c28d2","tid":166340,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:23:34.000Z","msg":"努力D寫故<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a60d1056c8d6c9fed263239e0ab6c96571d2db5","tid":166340,"uid":93755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:38:35.000Z","msg":"巴打加油"},{"pid":"0127c2b01c2448e61e89bde086acaeb34172b224","tid":166340,"uid":68811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T02:23:40.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<br />\n<br />\nBtw 張圖好靚 好有意思"},{"pid":"a160699ea728c16f2d3120fb016400e6634b285e","tid":166340,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T02:25:15.000Z","msg":"圖好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\